---
description: Landing page copy and UX conversion rules
globs: ["src/components/pages/LandingPageElite.tsx"]
alwaysApply: true
---
H1: max 8 words, outcome-first, zero jargon
BANNED IN HEADLINES: seamless, powerful, intuitive, robust,
  leverage, unlock, supercharge, next-level, game-changer,
  AI-powered, revolutionize
COPY RATIO: you/your >= 3x we/our
CTA: exactly one primary CTA per page view
DEMO: inline interactive energy-matching widget, no signup
READING LEVEL: Hemingway grade 7, short sentences, active voice
SOCIAL PROOF: real names + titles only, never anonymous
